modName: Lilly Female Courier with Tembtra Thief Armor
summary: This is just a small addon for the wonderfull mod Lilly - A fully-voiced female courier replacer by AlpineYJ and cald123 of Intracloud Productions
descriptionHtml:
This is just a small addon for the wonderfull mod Lilly - A fully-voiced female courier replacer by AlpineYJ and cald123 of Intracloud Productions that add the Tembtra Thief Armor UNP - CBBE to the lilly outfit

all credits go to the creators of the tow mods i have just added armor with tes5edit

Installation:

Downlaod and install [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/download/1000171932]Lilly - Female Courier Replacer[/url]
Download and install my file
Download and install [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/download/1000134937]D. Tembtra Thief Armor 2K CBBE[/url] non hdt ( you can disable the esp, the mod need just textures and meshes)
Endorse
Enjoy
